<h1>News</h1>

<div class="helper">
	<h2>Latest News</h2>
	<div>
		<p class="rationale">Show a number of the latest news items, with the newest at the top.</p>
		<p>Each news-story excerpt would consist of:</p>
		<ul class="content-types">
			<li>Title of news item</li>
			<li>Short excerpt</li>
			<li>Small thumbnail picture (optional)</li>
			<li>Link to the <a href="/news/news-item.html">full news item</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="helper">
	<h2>Categories</h2>
	<div>
		<p class="rationale">List the categories under which News can be posted. This acts as a quick way for people to narrow the list to topics they're interested in.</p>
		<p>Listed alphabetically for easy scanning, each list item would be:</p>
		<ul class="content-types">
			<li>Title of category</li>
			<li>Link to the <a href="/news/category.html">category</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>

